Package: dalycareatlas
Type: Package
Title: Aggregate DALY-CARE Atlas and Source Cartography
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alexander Owen", "Taylor", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Builds aggregate-only source cartography and static atlas bundles for
    DALY-CARE resources. The package profiles source availability, schema, code
    coverage, and high-level feature coverage without emitting patient-level rows.
